      "content": "it just feels pointless though. what \"new self\" is there? there's just this hollow, broken thing that everyone's looking at with pity. it's actually more exhausting trying to pretend to be okay than it would be to just stop. everything feels so much heavier than it should. it's like the light just went out and i'm just waiting for the dark to finish the job.",
